  "general_provisions": "This bill addresses audiovisual coverage of a court proceeding.",
  "hilighted_provisions": "This bill:<hr><ltbullet>defines terms;<hr><ltbullet>requires the Administrative Office of the Courts to provide a livestream of certain court proceedings for public observation;<hr><ltbullet>provides exceptions to the requirement to provide a livestream;<hr><ltbullet>requires the Administrative Office of the Courts to create an audiovisual recording of each livestream and make the recording freely available for public observation; and<hr><ltbullet>makes technical and conforming changes.",
